title: Amy Winehouse - Frank 2003
description:
A double disk set of Amy Winehouse's Frank, released in 2003.

CD 1 contains the following songs:

1. Intro (Stronger Than Me)
2. You Sent Me Flying - Cherry
3. Know You Now
4. Fuck Me Pumps
5. I Heard Love Is Blind
6. Moody's Mood For Love 
7. (There is) No Greater Love
8. In My Bed
9. Take The Box
10. October Song
11. What is it About Men
12. Help Yourself
13. Amy, Amy, Amy (Outro)

And the second CD contains original demos, live performances, and songs not released. 
Sit back, and enjoy these lovely songs. :)
